动期间作为战利品专属发布。","rarities":[{"region":"riot","rarity":1}]}],"emblems":null,"regionRarityId":0,"rarityGemPath":null,"skinLines":[{"id":191}],"description":"作为一名周围环绕着萤火虫魔宠的宫廷大贤者，米利欧对宫墙内发生的一切了如指掌。他可能看起来像个孩子，但花仙是长寿的，并且米利欧在儿童时期的时间远远超过其他人在成年人时期的时间。尽管如此，他还是挂着友善面孔，尽其所能地利用自己的力量来保护这个王国。"},{"id":902011,"contentId":"9cf4177d-a1e8-4fec-b240-4bb88cffe673","isBase":false,"name":"青蛙雨衣 米利欧","skinClassification":"kChampion","splashPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Milio/Skins/Skin11/Images/milio_splash_centered_11.SKINS_Milio_Skin11.jpg","uncenteredSplashPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Milio/Skins/Skin11/Images/milio_splash_uncentered_11.SKINS_Milio_Skin11.jpg","tilePath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Milio/Skins/Skin11/Images/milio_splash_tile_11.SKINS_Milio_Skin11.jpg","loadScreenPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Milio/Skins/Skin11/MilioLoadScreen_11.SKINS_Milio_Skin11.jpg","skinType":"","rarity":"kEpic","isLegacy":false,"splashVideoPath":null,"previewVideoUrl":null,"collectionSplashVideoPath":null,"collectionCardHoverVideoPath":null,"featuresText":null,"chromaPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/v1/champion-chroma-images/902/902011.png","chromas":[{"id":902012,"name":"青蛙雨衣 米利欧 红雨","contentId":"73744261-2f22-4789-a7a3-ec2ff6a42491","skinClassification":"kRecolor","chromaPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/v1/champion-chroma-images/902/902012.png","tilePath":"/lol-game-data/assets/v1/champion-chroma-images/902/902012.png","colors":["#D33528","#D33528"],"descriptions":[{"region":"riot","description":"这个炫彩曾在2024年期间作为礼包专属发布。"}],"description":"这个炫彩曾在2024年期间作为礼包专属发布。","rarities":[{"region":"riot","rarity":1}]},{"id":902013,"name":"青蛙雨衣 米利欧 喜雨","contentId":"3218b3ec-b8b2-4d20-a8eb-2da6ec68b6c4","skinClassification":"kRecolor","chromaPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/v1/champion-chroma-images/902/902013.png","tilePath":"/lol-game-data/assets/v1/champion-chroma-images/902/902013.png","colors":["#DF9117","#DF9117"],"descriptions":[],"description":"","rarities":